{"_id":"00huse2552esuh00","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"153","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.voice-of-the-spirits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":7,"folderName":"The Smile in the Darkness","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Voz de los espíritus","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber estado en contacto con los dones Espíritu o Espiritista.</p><p>Al calmar la mente y concentrarte, puedes abrirla al mundo espiritual y comunicarte con almas sin descanso. Gasta 1 Soma para contactar con una criatura que tenga el don Espíritu y a la que hayas encontrado previamente. Puedes comunicarte con el espíritu y entender lo que dice.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The Smile in the Darkness","requirements":"haber estado en contacto con los dones Espíritu o Espiritista.","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness"},"scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"157"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> You have been in contact with either the Spirit or Spiritualist Gifts.</p><p>With the right peace and focus, you can open your mind to the spirit world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact any creature with the Spirit Gift that you’ve previously encountered. You can communicate with the Spirit and understand what it says.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The Smile in the Darkness","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"The Smile in the Darkness","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.voice-of-the-spirits","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","sourceDirectory":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"You have been in contact with either the Spirit or Spiritualist Gifts.","limitations":""},"sort":700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"012rme2nn2emr210","name":"Exorcist","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"153","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.exorcist","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":8,"folderName":"The Smile in the Darkness","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Exorcista","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> tener un descriptor relacionado con la Iglesia o la magia. Hablar con Adrien o Alizée sobre las prácticas utilizadas contra los espíritus.</p><p>Has aprendido a utilizar tus habilidades contra los espíritus. Todas tus acciones pueden afectar a un objetivo que tenga el don Espíritu y todas las Heridas que inflijas no pueden ser ignoradas por ese don.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The Smile in the Darkness","requirements":"tener un descriptor relacionado con la Iglesia o la magia. Hablar con Adrien o Alizée sobre las prácticas utilizadas contra los espíritus.","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness"},"scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"157"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Have a Church or Magic-related Descriptor. Talk to Adrien or Alizée about practices used against Spirits.</p><p>You have learned how to use your skills against the Spirits. All your actions can affect a target who has the Spirit Gift and all Wounds you inflict cannot be ignored by the Spirit Gift.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The Smile in the Darkness","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"The Smile in the Darkness","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.exorcist","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","sourceDirectory":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Have a Church or Magic-related Descriptor. Talk to Adrien or Alizée about practices used against Spirits.","limitations":""},"sort":800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
